    @*DISPLAY HEADER LAYOUT*@
    <div class="display-header-layout container-fluid mb-5">
        <div class="container-sm heading-container">
            <div class="heading-line"></div>
            <h1 class="heading-with-lines display-1">The White Tiger</h1>
            <div class="heading-line"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    @*LINE & PARAGRAPH LAYOUT (LEFT)*@
    <div class="quote-layout container-fluid mb-5">
        <div class="container-sm">
            <div class="d-flex quote-layout-container" style="gap: 20px;">
                <div class="line"></div>
                <div class="quote-text-div">
                    <h3>
                        About Us
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        This is the White Tiger Farm & Restaurant. Here, we grow our own food under the warm climate of Dallas, Texas to promote plant-based sustainability. Our farms grow a wide range of crops to suuport our restaurants, and we are constantly evaluating what items are in demand to adjust our crop output accordingly. 
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The White Tiger Team is a capable, experienced team of farmers, planters, chefs, coordinators, and leaders with the goal of taking eating to a new high by utlizing Indian tradition and plant-based power to solve the modern imperative for plant-based sustainability. It is our promise to maintain a healthy, tasteful, and sustainable environment to allow our customers to enjoy the cuisine of the future. Have fun going through our website!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

